00:45:22,600 --> 00:45:30,800
Because Fliction provides these beautiful everyday analogies that prove we actually live in this reality every single day.

700
00:45:31,000 --> 00:45:35,640
If we truly live in an irreversible universe governed by collapse,

701
00:45:36,220 --> 00:45:40,080
it must leave observable signatures in our daily lives.

702
00:45:40,080 --> 00:45:48,060
The biggest and most obvious one is the profound asymmetry between prediction and reconstruction.

703
00:45:48,400 --> 00:45:48,840
Right.

704
00:45:49,220 --> 00:45:57,820
It is incredibly easy to predict that a raw egg dropped from a two-story roof will shatter on the pavement.

